Function Equivalent  GetCurrentProcessToken OpenProcessToken(GetCurrentProcess())  GetCurrentThreadToken OpenThreadToken(GetCurrentThread())  GetCurrentThreadEffectiveToken OpenThreadToken(GetCurrentThread()) + OpenProcessToken(GetCurrentProcess())  These pseudo-handles are handy because they can be obtained quickly and don’t need to be closed.

Title: Taiwan's amazing bike-sharing system
Description:
YouBike (or Ubike) is my first choice of transportation when it comes to moving around the city of Taipei. I largely prefer it over taking the subway, bus, or taxi. It is affordable, well maintained, comfortable, at waking distance reach from anywhere, and the cities have built great biking paths in the major cities.
